ague| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox sport tournament\n| name = [[EHF Champions League]]\n| year = 2000\u201301\n| image =\n| caption = \n| sport = [[Handball]]\n| location =\n| start_date =\n| end_date =\n| administrator =\n| tournament_format =\n| host =\n| venues =\n| participants =\n| purse =\n| champions = [[SDC San Antonio]]\n| matches =\n| previous = [[1999\u20132000 EHF Champions League|1999\u20132000]]\n| next = [[2001\u201302 EHF Champions League|2001\u201302]]\n}}\nThe '''2000\u201301 [[EHF Champions League]]''' was the 41st edition of [[Europe]]'s premier club [[Team handball|handball]] tournament.\n\n==Round 1==\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n!width=200|Team #1\n!width=50|Agg.\n!width=200|Team #2\n!width=100|1st match\n!width=100|2nd match\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[ASK\u0130 SK]]'''|Turkey| '''58''' : 41 |[[Granitas Kaunas]]|LTU| 29 : 18 | 29 : 23}}\n{{TwoLegResult| [[HC Berchem]] |LUX| 44 : '''68''' |'''[[Hapoel Rishon LeZion (handball)|Hapo\u00ebl Rishon LeZion]]'''|ISR| 25 : 31 | 19 : 37}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[GKS Wybrze\u017ce Gda\u0144sk|Wybrze\u017ce Gda\u0144sk]]''' |POL| '''53''' : 46 |[[SKP Secovce]]|SVK| 30 : 22 | 23 : 24}}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[SKA Minsk]]'''|BLR| '''52''' : 42 |[[HV Aalsmeer|HV Fiqas Aalsmeer]]|NED| 28 : 20 | 24 : 22 }}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[Haukar Handball|Haukar Hafnarfj\u00f6r\u00f0ur]]'''|ISL| '''53''' : 48 |[[HC Eynatten]]|BEL| 22 : 18 | 31 : 30 }}\n{{TwoLegResult| [[SPE Strovolos Nicosie]] |CYP| 50 : '''51''' |'''[[Remus B\u00e4rnbach-K\u00f6flach]]'''|AUT| 26 : 27 | 24 : 24  }}\n{{TwoLegResult| '''[[CSA Steaua Alexandrion Bucure\u0219ti (handball)|Steaua Bucarest]]''' |ROU| '''57''' : 52 |[[Panell\u00ednios Ath\u00e8nes (handball)|Panell\u00ednios Ath\u00e8nes]]|GRE| 30 \u2013 26 | 27 : 26 }}\n{{TwoLegResult| [[HRK Izvi\u0111a\u010d|Izvi\u0111a\u010d Ljubu\u0161ki]] |BIH| 41 : '''54''' |'''[[ZTR Zaporizhia]]'''|UKR| 23 : 24 | 18 : 30 }}\n|}\n\n==Round 2==\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n